{"tid":1680381,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[幫推］op罷工一事炒車呀","createTime":"2019-10-28T19:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T17:10:33.000Z","uid":161560,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8258e20f97070c8b205cbf8308c4d6e632aaeba9","tid":1680381,"uid":161560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T19:07:53.000Z","msg":"首先喺度道歉先，個po出得太快<br />\n唔完善，所以作出改善<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二，個po睇及嘅人名Eva 並非藍絲而係內部高層，出得太快，人為出錯，希望還返佢一個公道，推得太快收唔切<br />\n講返聲對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n批得個show出街嘅都係有良知的人，還返佢一個公道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第三，希望各位手足唔好參與，因為原意係想內部員工參與，位置亦十分危險，唔預計有咁大迴響<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重點係個人都認為太子手足都好重要</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關於海洋公園罷工一事會一更加多嘅資源喺內部公海流出"},{"pid":"4fcc92e0b19e64ab471b275db7597526926d3154","tid":1680381,"uid":311238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T19:08:25.000Z","msg":"救人呀！！有手足想自殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680356</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6148056d059f3d9844becfdf7231a24c9674b26c","tid":1680381,"uid":161560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T19:12:40.000Z","msg":"個罷工一事依然會繼續進行，亦有演員們嘅訴求<br />\n將會有更詳細整合<br />\n<br />\n現時只係想有啲嘢澄清番，並為被點名員工作致深出道歉"},{"pid":"6a9138a92d10c5db84608f3dda1d5e90f8e8c50a","tid":1680381,"uid":161560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T19:16:00.000Z","msg":"大家幫幫推，推返行動po<br />\n<br />\n同埋幫我還返Eva一個清白"},{"pid":"7399d7f1b6ee8342531edba11a739f84041eed73","tid":1680381,"uid":312526,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T19:19:12.000Z","msg":"但我想係op靜坐<br />\n多d人先保護到你地<br />\n同埋人多先有新聞"},{"pid":"b73030b42d9d7a6f6c4135d061bb86f695794f9a","tid":1680381,"uid":161560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,